You.

99
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:16,040
Look,

100
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,760
with all those years

101
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:18,920
in Mingke House,

102
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,760
gauging people's mind
and associating with countless people,

103
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:22,390
how could you fall for someone

104
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:23,000
like Han Muzhi,

105
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,790
who would do whatever it takes

106
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:25,510
