128
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,350
He's been so indifferent to you.

129
00:06:57,350 --> 00:06:58,440
Why do you defend him?

130
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,600
In this world,

131
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,670
