139
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,270
Are you feeling better?

140
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:52,640
Come here.

141
00:07:54,230 --> 00:07:55,270
Take it slow.

142
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,720
Young Master, are you feeling better?

143
