159
00:08:33,470 --> 00:08:34,590
Miss Luo.

160
00:08:34,590 --> 00:08:35,710
You're finally back.

161
00:08:35,710 --> 00:08:36,470
Baozi.

162
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,320
Good news.

163
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,710
Miss Liu and Mr. Liu

164
