207
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:21,080
If this removal papers

208
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:23,030
is really important to her,

209
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,790
I'm sure she'll be willing to

210
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,080
