226
00:14:27,590 --> 00:14:28,440
Lv Cong,

227
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,960
tell the truth.

228
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:32,710
Yes, Your Honor.

229
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:36,840
That day, Mr. Wu came to me

230
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,640
