235
00:14:43,230 --> 00:14:45,350
After that, there were two scapegoats

236
00:14:45,350 --> 00:14:46,520
in Hejin County Jail.

237
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,880
Mr. Wu said everything was settled.

238
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:49,840
He asked me

239
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,470
to take the notice he got from Hejin

240
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:54,230
and beat the drum
outside the court here.

241
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:55,840
Mr. Wu.

242
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,110
Do you plead guilty?

243
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:02,910
I'm just an old man

244
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,350
