245
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:07,230
How could I have the ability

246
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:09,280
to overturn for someone?

247
00:15:09,470 --> 00:15:10,670
Do you know Song

248
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,520
in Hejin County Jail?

249
00:15:13,710 --> 00:15:14,440
Yes.

250
00:15:15,470 --> 00:15:16,670
He confessed

251
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,470
that you went to see him last month,

252
00:15:18,470 --> 00:15:21,280
abetting him to get two bandits
for collusion.

253
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:23,080
That's a slander.

254
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,200
He's so vicious.

255
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:26,320
I had a relapse last month

256
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,760
and had been bedridden at home.

257
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,670
I didn't go to Hejin last month.

258
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:33,840
This is Jailer Song's testimony.

259
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,960
Do you want to see it yourself?

260
00:15:36,110 --> 00:15:37,710
I also have witnesses.

261
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:40,400
My wife, neighbors,

262
00:15:40,470 --> 00:15:42,550
and the shopkeeper of the pharmacy

263
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:44,840
can all testify for me.

264
00:15:45,590 --> 00:15:47,710
Your Honor,

265
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,840
my husband

266
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,760
was indeed ill last month.

267
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:52,280
I can testify.

268
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:53,110
Every morning,

269
00:15:53,110 --> 00:15:54,520
I saw Mrs. Wu

270
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:55,710
pouring out medicine dregs at the door.

271
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:56,910
Mr. Wu bought medicine

272
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:58,320
from my pharmacy last month.

273
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,400
He had cold-dampness syndrome.

274
00:15:59,590 --> 00:16:00,200
Your Honor,

275
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:03,440
to clear themselves,

276
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:05,230
these two framed me,

277
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:06,840
an old man nearing the end of life.

278
00:16:07,550 --> 00:16:08,590
Your Honor,

279
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:10,910
please punish them for false accusation.

280
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:11,640
You...

281
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:12,470
You!

282
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:16,280
You distort the facts!

283
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:19,000
It was you.

284
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,520
With the sky above as my witness,

285
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:22,440
Your Honor,

286
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:24,150
please restore my innocence

287
00:16:24,910 --> 00:16:25,760
and uphold justice today.

288
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:28,880
I...

289
00:16:29,230 --> 00:16:30,400
Father.

290
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:31,790
Are you okay?

